title: Governor Cuomo, Mayor de Blasio and MTA Chairman Prendergast Announce Agreement on Funding for MTA ...
text: ( Source : MTA - Metropolitan Transportation Authority ) Governor Andrew M. Cuomo, Mayor Bill de Blasio and MTA Chairman Tom Prendergast today announced that an agreement has been reached on the remaining funding for the MTA Capital Program .
